> (parameterize ([print-gensym #t])
    (pretty-print (list (gensym) (gensym))))
(#@{g2 |KR1M2&CTt1<B0n/m|@} #@{g3 |FBAb&7NC6&=c82!O|@})

> (parameterize ([print-gensym 'pretty])
    (pretty-print (list (gensym) (gensym))))
(#:g4 #:g5)
@end example

The initial value of @code{print-gensym} is @true{}.

