first example with the output of the examples below:

@example
> (pretty-print
    (parameterize ([gensym-prefix "var"] [print-gensym #f])
      (list (gensym) (gensym) (gensym))))
(g3 g4 g5)

> (let ([ls (list (gensym) (gensym) (gensym))])
    (parameterize ([gensym-prefix "var"] [print-gensym #f])
